<title>UK: CRT buys IKPG for 23.8 mln stg.</title>
<headline>CRT buys IKPG for 23.8 mln stg.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-03-18</dateline>
<text>
<p>UK training and recruitment firm CRT Group Plc said on Tuesday it had bought IKPG, an IT contract and permanent recruitment company, for 23.8 million stg.  </p>
<p>CRT said in a statement that the payment will be in cash, loan notes and CRT shares at 232p per share. IKPG will be merged with its IT recruitment company, Software Personnel.</p>
